Package permafrost.tundra.io.filter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndFilenameFilter
    Chains multiple FilenameFilter objects with a logical AND operation.
    ConditionalFilenameFilter
    An abstract FilenameFilter that chains together other filters.
    DirectoryFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that only accepts directories.
    DirectoryFilenameFilter.Holder
    Initialization on demand holder idiom.
    ExclusionFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter which accepts files that do not match the patterns in this filter.
    FileFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that only accepts files.
    FileFilenameFilter.Holder
    Initialization on demand holder idiom.
    FilenameFilterHelper
    A collection of convenience methods for FilenameFilter objects.
    InclusionFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter which accepts files which match the patterns in this filter.
    LiteralFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter which matches the given literal.
    NotFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that negates another FilenameFilter.
    OrFilenameFilter
    Chains multiple FilenameFilter objects with a logical OR operation.
    RegularExpressionFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that only accepts objects whose names match the given regular expression.
    WildcardFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that only accepts objects that match the given wildcard expression.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FilenameFilterType
    The different types of filename filters supported by the InclusionFilenameFilter and ExclusionFilenameFilter classes.
